      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative vehicle, maintained to an exacting standard that defies its age. This specimen remains in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, offering the discerning collector or enthusiast an unparalleled driving experience. This is an acquisition for those who demand nothing less than automotive perfection.",
