    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! The paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it runs like a total dream. It\u2019s super rare to find one in this kind of condition, and I\u2019m so excited for it to go to a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43900.0,
