      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'mint condition.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a day of inclement weather. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every body panel is original with perfect factory alignment. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the hand-stitched leather seats show absolutely no signs of wear or creasing, and the interior still carries a faint hint of the original factory scent. All technological features, from the premium surround-sound system to the advanced driver-assist suite, operate with precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized dealerships\u2014full service logs are included. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, and the undercarriage remains in showroom state. This is a collector-grade example suited for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection without compromise.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
